Package: stegovault
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: StegoVault Team <shokhai2007@gmail.com>
Depends: python3, python3-venv, python3-pip
Description: Digital Steganography Vault (File-in-Image & Zero-Width Text)
 A tool to hide any binary file within an image using 2-bit LSB steganography
 and invisible text within messages using non-rendering Unicode characters.
